{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)resume","title":"resume","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a pack resumes after being suspended, it may begin by iterating over the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"already downloaded resources. As a result, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" structure’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"countOfResourcesCompleted"},{"type":"text","text":" field may revert to 0 before rapidly returning to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the level of progress at the time the pack was suspended."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To temporarily suspend downloading, call the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-suspend"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/resume"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Resumes downloading if the pack is inactive.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/resume"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/resume":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/resume","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Resumes downloading if the pack is inactive.","type":"text"}],"title":"resume","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/resume","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePack"}}}